pharaoh 's curse is a 1957 american horror film directed by lee sholem and written by richard h. landau .   the film stars mark dana , ziva rodann , diane brewster , george n. neise , alvaro guillot and ben wright .   the film was released in february 1957 , by united artists .   archaeologists in egypt find one of their crew has been turned into a blood sucking mummy after they have unleashed a three thousand year curse by entering a pharaoh 's tomb .